description: Demolition of existing buildings and re-provision of two-storey building to accommodate a nursery (with associated external amenity play space) and community centre (Use Class D1); provision of 126 new residential units (16 x 3-bedroom part two/part three storey townhouses, and 110 units (93 x 1-bedroom and 17 x 2-bedroom) in 4 x blocks of flatted accommodation ranging from three to five storeys in height); associated landscaping; car parking; widening of vehicular access to site; and provision of new pedestrian access routes to Downhills Park (the application is a Departure from the Development Plan).
